---
layout: base.njk
pageTitle: 活動報告
permalink: /activities/index.html
---
<main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-8">
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-kon mb-2 border-l-4 border-midori pl-3">活動報告</h1>
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">各グループの活動記録です。</p>
  <div class="space-y-4">
    {% for item in collections.activities %}
    <article class="border rounded-lg p-4 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
        {% if item.data.group == "hana" %}<span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-bold">花の会</span>
        {% elif item.data.group == "tokiwa" %}<span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-bold">ときわ会</span>
        {% elif item.data.group == "hibari" %}<span class="bg-pink-100 text-pink-800 text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-bold">ひばり会</span>
        {% elif item.data.group == "bohan" %}<span class="bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-800 text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-bold">防犯部</span>
        {% endif %}
        <time class="text-sm text-gray-500">{{ item.date | dateJp }}</time>
      </div>
      <a href="{{ item.url }}" class="font-bold text-base hover:underline text-kon block">{{ item.data.title }}</a>
    </article>
    {% else %}
    <p class="text-gray-500">活動報告はまだありません。</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</main>
